{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01WqSH1dYCvcSyDivmiMvCXt","type":"tool_result","content":"   358→// These cover the most common recipe instruction starters. Includes common OCR-corrupted\n   359→// forms (e.g., \"Smaż\" → \"Smaz\", \"Dodaj\" → \"Dodaj\").\n   360→// Note: only verbs that NEVER start a recipe title. \"Piecz\" (bake) is excluded because\n   361→// \"Pieczeń\" (roast) and \"Pieczarki\" (mushrooms) share the prefix.\n   362→const POLISH_COOKING_INSTRUCTION_STARTS = /^(podawaj|dodaj|dodawaj|sma[zż]|gotuj|odced[zź]|wymieszaj|mieszaj|wlej|nalej|przygotuj|zagotuj|pokr[oó]j|obierz|wrzuc|wrzuć|usma[zż]|podsma[zż]|prze[lł][oó][zż]|zblenduj|ubij|roztrzepaj|rozprowad[zź]|wyrob|zamieszaj|posyp|polej|odstaw|na[lł][oó][zż]|przykryj|odkryj|wstaw|zdejmij|ods[aą]cz|rozgrzej|posiekaj|zetrzyj|wy[lł][oó][zż]|wyjmij|ukr[oó]j|przekr[oó]j|formuj|ugniataj|rozwałkuj|ugotuj|ugotowa[cć]|upiecz|podawa[cć]|zapiekaj|obtocz|obtoczy[cć]|podgrzej|podgrzewaj)\\b/i;\n   363→\n   364→function looksLikeCookingInstruction(text: string): boolean {\n   365→  const words = text.trim().split(/\\s+/);\n   366→  // Polish cooking instructions are commonly 2-3 words (\"Ugotuj ziemniaki.\", \"Upiecz chleb.\")\n   367→  // and are unambiguous because Polish recipe titles don't start with imperative verbs.\n   368→  if (POLISH_COOKING_INSTRUCTION_STARTS.test(text.trim())) {\n   369→    return words.length >= 2;  // Polish: 2+ words is enough\n   370→  }\n   371→  if (words.length < 4) return false;  // English: keep existing 4-word threshold\n   372→  if (COOKING_INSTRUCTION_STARTS.test(text.trim())) return true;\n   373→  return false;\n   374→}\n   375→\n   376→/**\n   377→ * A line starting with a lowercase letter and having 4+ words is prose continuation.\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4407852d-7747-4d05-8f35-a479d23762b1","uuid":"9e4479e8-5b6a-4fec-a849-1e976d11389f","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/lib/text-classifier/title-extractor.ts","content":"// These cover the most common recipe instruction starters. Includes common OCR-corrupted\n// forms (e.g., \"Smaż\" → \"Smaz\", \"Dodaj\" → \"Dodaj\").\n// Note: only verbs that NEVER start a recipe title. \"Piecz\" (bake) is excluded because\n// \"Pieczeń\" (roast) and \"Pieczarki\" (mushrooms) share the prefix.\nconst POLISH_COOKING_INSTRUCTION_STARTS = /^(podawaj|dodaj|dodawaj|sma[zż]|gotuj|odced[zź]|wymieszaj|mieszaj|wlej|nalej|przygotuj|zagotuj|pokr[oó]j|obierz|wrzuc|wrzuć|usma[zż]|podsma[zż]|prze[lł][oó][zż]|zblenduj|ubij|roztrzepaj|rozprowad[zź]|wyrob|zamieszaj|posyp|polej|odstaw|na[lł][oó][zż]|przykryj|odkryj|wstaw|zdejmij|ods[aą]cz|rozgrzej|posiekaj|zetrzyj|wy[lł][oó][zż]|wyjmij|ukr[oó]j|przekr[oó]j|formuj|ugniataj|rozwałkuj|ugotuj|ugotowa[cć]|upiecz|podawa[cć]|zapiekaj|obtocz|obtoczy[cć]|podgrzej|podgrzewaj)\\b/i;\n\nfunction looksLikeCookingInstruction(text: string): boolean {\n  const words = text.trim().split(/\\s+/);\n  // Polish cooking instructions are commonly 2-3 words (\"Ugotuj ziemniaki.\", \"Upiecz chleb.\")\n  // and are unambiguous because Polish recipe titles don't start with imperative verbs.\n  if (POLISH_COOKING_INSTRUCTION_STARTS.test(text.trim())) {\n    return words.length >= 2;  // Polish: 2+ words is enough\n  }\n  if (words.length < 4) return false;  // English: keep existing 4-word threshold\n  if (COOKING_INSTRUCTION_STARTS.test(text.trim())) return true;\n  return false;\n}\n\n/**\n * A line starting with a lowercase letter and having 4+ words is prose continuation.","numLines":20,"startLine":358,"totalLines":1745}}}
